    "d881b49f46d205a1649c9c5c8c7497bfdfa4bac948575a46901a6fe9c2b10364": "Excellent! Well then, [?], I'm pleased to say that we have the results of your interview. You bring some impressive stuff to the table. We'd love to offer you the role!",
